<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Congratulations Page</title>
    <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .congratulations-container {
            border: 2px solid #FFD700; /* Golden color */
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 20px;
            max-width: 600px; /* Optional: Set maximum width */
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
            margin: auto; /* Center the container */
        }

        /* Optional: Add some additional styling */
        .congratulations-heading {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .congratulations-text {
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin: 0 auto; /* Center the text */
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
    <div class="congratulations-container">
        <h2 class="congratulations-heading mx-auto">Congratulations on completing your SWOT analysis!</h2>
        <p class="congratulations-text mx-auto">We are pleased to inform you that your company has been doing really well in terms of seeking opportunities. Your strength percentage was really appreciable. We hope that this analysis would have given you a clear view of where your company stands. All the best for your future endeavors, and hope to see you again.</p>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- Bootstrap JS and jQuery (if needed) -->
<script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.2.1.slim.min.js"></script>
<script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>

</body>
</html>
